        "text": "Return the skillet with reserved bacon fat to medium-high heat, add olive oil if pan is dry, then add ground beef. Break into crumbles and cook without overcrowding until browned, about 5–7 minutes; season with garlic powder, onion powder, salt, and pepper during cooking.",
